Hi, Stoffer.
嗨，史托佛

66
00:06:20,480000 --> 00:06:25,160000
Hi. Now we get out of the car again, right?
我们又要下车了

67
00:06:25,160000 --> 00:06:29,680000
Are you the person I talked to? Welcome to the factory.
我跟你讲过电话？ 对 欢迎参观工厂

68
00:06:29,680000 --> 00:06:33,977000
Oh, you've brought a wheelchair?
你们带了轮椅？ 对

69
00:06:38,280000 --> 00:06:41,889000
Don't leave her behind.
别把她丢在后面

70
00:06:53,720000 --> 00:06:58,120000
It may sound a bit a bit dull.
听起来或许…有点无聊

71
00:06:58,120000 --> 00:07:05,196000
But when you get to know it, it's actually a fascinating product.
其实这是很有趣的产品

72
00:07:05,400000 --> 00:07:09,719000
Hey, no, no! You mustn't do that.
不，不 不要碰

73
00:07:09,920000 --> 00:07:10,824000
Watch this!
不要

74
00:07:10,824000 --> 00:07:18,947000
I'm going to stop the entire production of Rockwool in Denmark.
你们看 我要关掉全丹麦的岩纤维生产

75
00:07:20,080000 --> 00:07:24,400000
- And it stops. - No!
停了 不

76
00:07:24,400000 --> 00:07:29,160000
- No! - Don't worry.
不要 别担心

77
00:07:29,160000 --> 00:07:33,039000
Hey, you! Come over here! Don't be frightened.
你，过来，别怕

78
00:07:33,240000 --> 00:07:37,233000
Press the green button. Do you see it? Come on!
按绿色钮，看到没？

79
00:07:38,880000 --> 00:07:36,129000
And the production starts again.

80
00:07:36,129000 --> 00:07:38,798000
好棒哦

81
00:07:48,920000 --> 00:07:52,397000
It's fireproof, as you see. Nothing's on fire.
这能防火，不会着火

82
00:07:52,560000 --> 00:07:55,940000
Don't be frightened, nothing will happen, wait for the bang.
别怕，没事的

83
00:07:55,940000 --> 00:07:58,909000
看我开一枪

84
00:08:01,320000 --> 00:08:03,415000
Shall we have a soda? Yeah
我们喝点饮料吧

85
