Don't press that. Just let it hang there.
好 别按，不要去碰

86
00:08:13,720000 --> 00:08:18,669000
Now you've heard about Rockwool and how it works.
你们听了岩纤维的介绍

87
00:08:18,880000 --> 00:08:21,000000
