现在我问你们

88
00:08:21,000000 --> 00:08:23,863000
which of these houses is insulated with Rockwool?
哪一间房子装了岩纤维？

89
00:08:23,863000 --> 00:08:26,299000
Yes?
哪一间？

90
00:08:26,299000 --> 00:08:29,709000
Come on up
来吧

91
00:08:31,080000 --> 00:08:35,440000
