差不多

92
00:08:35,440000 --> 00:08:40,902000
Those who think this one is insulated with Rockwool, put your hands up.
觉得是这间的人请举手

93
00:08:43,960000 --> 00:08:47,089000
Rather a lot
很多人

94
00:08:47,280000 --> 00:08:50,960000
I think I can hear your minibus.
我听到你们的车来了

95
00:08:50,960000 --> 00:08:54,400000
I think they're leaving. Don't get left behind.
他们要走了，别跟不上

96
00:08:54,400000 --> 00:08:57,760000
There. That's the best place, almost.
这是最好的位子

97
00:08:57,760000 --> 00:08:59,316000
_ ' BYe~bye . - ' Bye .
再见

98
00:08:59,316000 --> 00:09:05,759000
That's the lot. Give us a hand, Karen.
再见 到了，帮个忙，凯伦

99
00:09:09,200000 --> 00:09:11,360000
Who is he driving?
他要开车？

100
00:09:11,360000 --> 00:09:15,911000
Responsibility does them good. No, not
让他们负责任是好的

101
00:09:32,000000 --> 00:09:35,960000
- ls that really a good idea? - No harm done, he's doing fine.
真的行吗？ 没事，他行的

102
00:09:35,960000 --> 00:09:39,193000
Reverse, reverse!
倒车，倒车

103
00:09:43,600000 --> 00:09:45,475000
Thanks for coming.
谢谢参观

104
00:09:45,475000 --> 00:09:48,444000
再见

105
00:09:49,680000 --> 00:09:54,451000
We have a driver Who is a nutter
我们有司机，是个神经病

106
00:09:54,451000 --> 00:09:58,878000
At our camp At our camp
在我们家里，在我们家里

107
00:09:59,080000 --> 00:10:03,835000
We have a driver Who is a nutter
我们有司机，是个神经病

108
00:10:04,040000 --> 00:10:06,760000
At our camp Where we are
在我们家里…

109
00:10:06,760000 --> 00:10:10,133000
What do you think?
你觉得如何？

110
00:10:10,560000 --> 00:10:14,103000
I don't think it was very funny.
我不觉得很好玩

111
00:10:15,240000 --> 00:10:17,800000
Why not?
为什么？

112
00:10:17,800000 --> 00:10:22,078000
You poke fun.
你们在作弄别人

113
00:10:30,880000 --> 00:10:37,260000
- They're the ones who poke fun. - Stoffer, cool it.
他们才在作弄我们 史托佛别闹

114
00:11:28,516000 --> 00:11:31,485000
Anders speaking.
我是安德斯

115
00:11:35,720000 --> 00:11:38,725000
Is that you, Karen?
凯伦，是你吗？

116
00:12:13,960000 --> 00:12:19,480000
Jeppe copped out right in the middle, and it pisses me off.
杰普中途打退堂鼓 真让人生气

117
00:12:19,480000 --> 00:12:22,440000
He didn't cop out.
他才没有

118
00:12:22,440000 --> 00:12:24,176000
- But you think so? - He wasn't there.
你说有？

119
00:12:24,176000 --> 00:12:27,160000
It was written all over his face.
他根本就没认真装傻

120
00:12:27,160000 --> 00:12:32,640000
You should fucking well play along.
你是个胆小鬼 没胆量跟我们一起扮白痴

121
00:12:32,640000 --> 00:12:35,000000
Leave him alone.
放过他吧

122
00:12:35,000000 --> 00:12:39,880000
Did you think I was bad, too?
你也觉得我装得不像？

123
00:12:39,880000 --> 00:12:43,509000
I wasn't watching anybody.
我没有看别人

124
00:12:43,720000 --> 00:12:46,800000
I was trying to feel it for myself.
我都自己去感受

125
00:12:46,800000 --> 00:12:53,308000
Surely that's allowed? I can't say whether you were good or bad.
我不知道你像不像

126
00:12:54,920000 --> 00:13:00,517000
What are you writing? That I was good or bad or ...?
你写什么？ 我装得像不像？

127
00:13:06,779000 --> 00:13:09,748000
I write that you were
我写你...

128
00:13:11,840000 --> 00:13:14,341000
Bad.
逊毙了

129
00:13:20,800000 --> 00:13:25,798000
You can sleep here if you want. There's enough room.
你可以在这里睡，地方够大

130
00:13:25,798000 --> 00:13:28,767000
I'm not going to sleep here.
我不想在这里睡

131
00:13:28,840000 --> 00:13:32,704000
I'd just like to sit a while.
我只想坐一会儿

132
00:13:34,040000 --> 00:13:36,760000
I thought Jeppe was good.
我觉得杰普装得很像

133
00:13:36,760000 --> 00:13:40,280000
- Where the hell was Jeppe good? - He was good by the machine.
他哪里像？

134
00:13:40,280000 --> 00:13:45,652000
He did fuck all by the machine. Fuck all.
他在机器旁边装傻 他在机器旁边像个白痴

135
00:13:45,652000 --> 00:13:47,087000
I know. That was what was so cool.
每部机器

136
00:13:47,087000 --> 00:13:50,056000
我知道，真酷

137
00:13:50,280000 --> 00:13:53,040000
A quick summary of what we were at?
简单说一下我们在干嘛？

138
00:13:53,040000 --> 00:13:57,680000
No, an understandable summary I've heard 17 different versions.
说个听得懂的 我已经听了十七个说法

139
00:13:57,680000 --> 00:14:01,400000
A quick summary? They wanted to fuck as many as possible -
他们要在最短时间惹毛所有人

140
00:14:01,400000 --> 00:14:06,561000
- as quickly as possible. Isn't that so, Axel?
对不对，艾克索？

141
00:14:07,840000 --> 00:14:10,311000
Axel says it was his idea. I think it was Stoffer's.
他说是他的点子

142
00:14:10,311000 --> 00:14:15,440000
It was my idea, but it was Stoffer
我觉得是史托佛的 是我的点子，是史托佛…

143
00:14:15,440000 --> 00:14:18,160000
who wanted to do something about it.
真的去做了

144
00:14:18,160000 --> 00:14:21,440000
That's funny; none of the others say it was your idea.
有意思，没人说是你的点子

145
00:14:21,440000 --> 00:14:24,400000
How come? None of them!
怎么会？一个都没有

146
00:14:24,400000 --> 00:14:29,480000
Would Stoffer also say it was a game?
史托佛也说是游戏吗？

147
00:14:29,480000 --> 00:14:31,666000
No, I don't think so.
不，不会吧

148
00:14:31,800000 --> 00:14:33,235000
- But it was? - Yes, it was, really.
到底是不是？

149
00:14:33,235000 --> 00:14:36,204000
当然是

150
00:14:58,800000 --> 00:15:02,698000
- Good morning. - Good morning, Honey.
早安

151
00:15:07,360000 --> 00:15:10,280000
- Good morning. - Good morning.
早 早安

152
00:15:10,280000 --> 00:15:14,273000
Axel, you have a visitor.
早安 艾克索，有人找你

153
00:15:14,273000 --> 00:15:17,916000
- Actually, it's Katrine. - Oh, shit.
什么？ 是凯瑟琳

154
00:15:18,010000 --> 00:15:22,400000
- Hi. - Hi, Katrine.
真烦 嗨，凯瑟琳

155
00:15:22,400000 --> 00:15:26,151000
Is there something I've got wrong? You didn't go to Jutland?
我弄错了吗？

156
00:15:26,151000 --> 00:15:27,386000
Sure. I've been to Jutland.
你没去尤特连？

157
00:15:27,386000 --> 00:15:32,600000
Because I thought this spassing about was pathetic.
当然去了 我觉得成天装白痴真悲哀

158
00:15:32,600000 --> 00:15:36,347000
- So what the hell are you back for? - I've changed my mind.
那你回来做什么？ 我改变主意了

159
00:15:36,400000 --> 00:15:40,517000
- "Changed your mind?" - Yes. ls that wrong?
改变主意？ 对 不行吗？

160
00:15:40,560000 --> 00:15:44,720000
You might have come to get me back again, right?
你是为了我回来的，对不对？

161
00:15:44,720000 --> 00:15:49,040000
What the hell would I see in you, man?
我看上你哪一点？

162
00:15:49,040000 --> 00:15:51,232000
- Oh, Katrine - You think very highly of yourself.
凯瑟琳

163
00:15:51,232000 --> 00:15:53,800000
Quit touching me.
你自以为了不起，别碰我

164
00:15:53,800000 --> 00:15:56,880000
Your lies are pouring out of every hole in your body.
你浑身上下充满谎言

165
00:15:56,880000 --> 00:15:59,240000
- What's your problem? - No problem.
你有什么意见？

166
00:15:59,240000 --> 00:16:02,277000
If that's the way you feel, come on.
我没意见 你好像很不爽

167
00:16:02,277000 --> 00:16:06,114000
You want to go outside? Fine.
你真这么觉得就来吧 你想出去吗？

168
00:16:06,114000 --> 00:16:10,269000
Stoffer?
好 史托佛？

169
00:16:10,605000 --> 00:16:12,874000
Axel is telling me to beat it.
艾克索叫我滚蛋

170
00:16:12,874000 --> 00:16:17,140000
Pretty weird when I've come to spass.
真奇怪，我不能装白痴吗？

171
00:16:17,160000 --> 00:16:20,311000
- She's come back to get at me. - Who has?
她是回来找我的 谁？

172
00:16:20,348000 --> 00:16:22,782000
Three guesses. Say something to her.
还有谁？你跟她说

173
00:16:22,840000 --> 00:16:29,280000
Katrine, have you come to spass or have you come to get Axel back?
凯瑟琳 你是来装白痴还是找艾克索？

174
00:16:29,280000 --> 00:16:32,589000
I've come to spass.
我来装白痴

175
00:16:32,794000 --> 00:16:35,763000
才怪

