他的画既挑衅又充满惊奇 没有人能挑你的毛病

1046
01:33:24,960000 --> 01:33:28,608000
Nobody could accuse you of that.
我得出去透透气

1047
01:33:28,720000 --> 01:33:32,680000
I need some air. - Hello! - Yes?
干嘛？

1048
01:33:32,680000 --> 01:33:37,400000
What's going on? Fuck all. You love this middle-class crap.
你在干嘛？ 你真爱这种中产阶级的玩意

1049
01:33:37,400000 --> 01:33:43,990000
These old biddies use more make-up than the National Theatre.
这群老女人搽的粉 比小丑还厚

1050
01:33:49,000000 --> 01:33:55,758000
It's lovely to have Henrik back, don't you think?

1051
01:34:08,320000 --> 01:33:51,801000
What happened?

1052
01:33:51,801000 --> 01:33:53,826000
汉瑞回来真好

1053
01:33:54,003000 --> 01:33:55,265000
真好

1054
01:34:13,023000 --> 01:34:17,161000
We didn't come to hear about a French faggot and his calligraphy.
我不是来听同性恋画家的事

1055
01:34:17,161000 --> 01:34:20,950000
It's too fucking bad.
怎么啦？ 给我闭嘴

1056
01:34:21,160000 --> 01:34:25,502000
- I tried. - You coughed three times.
他妈的糟糕透顶

1057
01:34:29,000000 --> 01:34:32,720000
- It wasn't that easy. - No.
我试了 并不容易

1058
01:34:32,720000 --> 01:34:37,768000
Stoffer is right. It wasn't good enough.
是啊 史托佛说得对，我不够认真 我对内心的白痴不觉得自傲

1059
01:34:37,768000 --> 01:34:40,404000
I had no pride in my inner idiot. I wasn't good enough.
我不够好 你是真的试过了

1060
01:34:40,404000 --> 01:34:44,954000
You did try.
我不跟你们回去了

1061
01:34:45,160000 --> 01:34:47,720000
I'm not coming back with you.

1062
01:34:59,240000 --> 01:35:02,209000
OK.
好吧

1063
01:35:23,560000 --> 01:35:26,279000
Ready yet?
好了吗？

1064
01:35:34,080000 --> 01:35:36,520000
Karen, my love.
凯伦，好好保重

1065
01:35:36,520000 --> 01:35:41,920000
Take care, now. Take care.
保重

1066
01:35:43,160000 --> 01:35:46,329000
Nana.“
娜娜

1067
01:35:47,480000 --> 01:35:51,960000
Let them go, Karen. It was all a lie.
让他们走，凯伦 一切都是空

1068
01:35:51,960000 --> 01:35:55,747000
I have something I want to say.
我有话要说

1069
01:36:00,220000 --> 01:36:03,309000
I just want to say
我只想说…

1070
01:36:04,325000 --> 01:36:07,294000
how happy I have been here.
我在这儿很快乐

1071
01:36:10,898000 --> 01:36:16,114000
Being an idiot with you is one of the best things I've ever done.
当白痴是我一生最棒的事

1072
01:36:18,640000 --> 01:36:21,675000
JePPe
杰普

1073
01:36:22,310000 --> 01:36:27,630000
who is almost like a little child I might have had.
简直像我的小孩

1074
01:36:27,783000 --> 01:36:30,987000
And Nana, -
娜娜

1075
01:36:30,987000 --> 01:36:34,624000
- who is so sweet and funny.
总是甜美又有趣

1076
01:36:34,624000 --> 01:36:37,627000
And Miguel, -
米格

1077
01:36:37,627000 --> 01:36:41,897000
- who has such lovely eyes.
有一对漂亮的眼睛

1078
01:36:41,897000 --> 01:36:47,149000
And Ped, who is such a clever man.
佩德 你是那么聪明

1079
01:36:49,071000 --> 01:36:53,519000
And strong, strong Katrine.
还有坚强的凯瑟琳

1080
01:37:00,483000 --> 01:37:03,452000
And Susanne
和苏珊

1081
01:37:05,388000 --> 01:37:17,799000
who smiles at everyone so that the very heavens shine down upon us. I believe
拥有像天使一般的笑容 我相信

1082
01:37:18,120000 --> 01:37:21,000000
I love you all -
我爱大家…胜过任何人

1083
01:37:21,000000 --> 01:37:25,357000
- more than I have ever loved anybody.
我爱大家…胜过任何人

1084
01:37:28,112000 --> 01:37:33,015000
Maybe with one exception. But that was so long ago now.
除了一个人，那是以前的事

1085
01:37:40,880000 --> 01:37:45,629000
- What day is it tomorrow? - It's Saturday.
明天礼拜几？ 礼拜六

1086
01:37:45,629000 --> 01:37:48,598000
对

1087
01:37:48,680000 --> 01:37:52,235000
Then it can be done.
那就没问题

1088
01:37:54,738000 --> 01:37:56,797000
什么事？

1089
01:37:58,800000 --> 01:38:12,439000
It is my turn to go home and see if I can be an idiot there. I suppose I'll need to take one of you along.
该我回家装傻当白痴 我需要一个人跟我做伴

1090
01:38:14,040000 --> 01:38:18,319000
But there isn't room for everyone.
我不能让每个人都去

1091
01:38:23,880000 --> 01:38:27,181000
It may not be very pleasant.
那会很不愉快

1092
01:38:32,560000 --> 01:38:36,759000
I think I'd like to take Susanne.
我想请苏珊陪我去

1093
01:38:39,680000 --> 01:38:43,116000
Will you come?
你愿意吗？

1094
01:38:43,320000 --> 01:38:46,569000
I'd like that.
我愿意

1095
01:38:49,800000 --> 01:38:53,129000
Good.
很好

1096
01:38:55,480000 --> 01:39:01,191000
We'll see if I can show you that it has all been worthwhile.
看我能不能证明这是值得的

1097
01:39:27,560000 --> 01:39:33,038000
- Hello, Mother. - Hello, Karen.
你好，妈 你好，凯伦

1098
01:39:37,360000 --> 01:39:40,679000
Come in.
进来

1099
01:39:45,553000 --> 01:39:48,522000
Shall I take your jacket?
外套交给我

1100
01:39:56,320000 --> 01:39:59,600000
Karen
凯伦

1101
01:39:59,840000 --> 01:40:03,435000
Where have you been?
你到哪儿了？

1102
01:40:03,640000 --> 01:40:06,800000
We thought you were dead.
我们以为你死了

1103
01:40:06,800000 --> 01:40:10,160000
This is Susanne.
她是苏珊

1104
01:40:10,160000 --> 01:40:13,747000
And my sister, Britta.
我妹妹，布丽塔

1105
01:40:17,820000 --> 01:40:20,789000
Louise?
露易丝？

1106
01:40:24,040000 --> 01:40:27,095000
Karen's come.
凯伦回来了

1107
01:40:29,360000 --> 01:40:32,360000
What do you want?
你要做什么？

1108
01:40:32,360000 --> 01:40:36,438000
I just wanted to see how you all were This is Susanne.
看看大家好不好

1109
01:40:36,438000 --> 01:40:41,880000
Anders is coming.
她是苏珊 安德斯要来

1110
01:40:41,880000 --> 01:40:45,647000
Yes, I suppose he is.
我猜也是

1111
01:40:46,000000 --> 01:40:49,469000
Karen, is that you?
凯伦，是你吗？

1112
01:40:49,480000 --> 01:40:52,487000
Yes, Grandpa.
是的，爷爷

1113
01:41:05,568000 --> 01:41:09,793000
We haven't seen her for two weeks.
我们有两星期没看到她

1114
01:41:14,044000 --> 01:41:19,316000
Not since the day before the funeral.
从葬礼到现在

1115
01:41:29,092000 --> 01:41:34,956000
Anders and Karen lost their little boy.
安德斯和凯伦的小孩过世

1116
01:41:36,120000 --> 01:41:40,192000
It probably hurt Anders most.
安德斯好像比较伤心

1117
01:41:40,800000 --> 01:41:46,031000
What with her just disappearing and not attending the funeral.
她连葬礼都没去就消失无踪

1118
01:42:22,200000 --> 01:42:25,357000
<i>MY pet </i>
别哭…

1119
01:42:43,520000 --> 01:42:46,159000
That'll be Anders.
是安德斯

1120
01:42:53,080000 --> 01:42:45,629000
- Hello, Grandpa. - Hello, Anders.

1121
01:42:45,629000 --> 01:42:48,598000
你好，安德斯

1122
01:43:00,000000 --> 01:43:03,289000
Hello, Anders.
安德斯

1123
01:43:03,320000 --> 01:43:06,559000
Hello, Karen.
你好，凯伦

1124
01:43:21,040000 --> 01:43:25,359000
I'm sorry I couldn't come to
抱歉我不能参加…

1125
01:43:25,920000 --> 01:43:29,390000
To Martin's funeral.
马丁的…葬礼

1126
01:43:30,400000 --> 01:43:34,080000
It just means you aren't too upset.
那表示你并不伤心

1127
01:43:34,080000 --> 01:43:37,413000
That's fine.
无所谓

1128
01:43:50,000000 --> 01:43:54,430000
Louise?
露易丝？

1129
01:44:20,600000 --> 01:44:25,461000
Do begin.
吃吧

1130
01:46:11,080000 --> 01:46:14,089000
That's enough now, Karen.
够了，凯伦

1131
01:46:24,720000 --> 01:46:28,637000
Shall we go?
我们走吧

1132
01:46:39,040000 --> 01:46:42,485000
Yes.
好

